   <text>
      <body divRole="original-translation">
         <div type="original" xml:lang="nl">
            <pb xml:id="pb.orig.nl.1" f="1r" facs="#s1r" n="1"/>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.1" n="1">Amst.</p>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.2" n="2">Zaterdag</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.3" n="3">Lieve Jo,</p>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.4" n="4">Wees zoo goed en kom ten spoedigste want ik wou een portret van je maken.<ptr type="note" target="#note.orig.nl.1"/> Maak dan als ’t kan dat je niet zoo vroeg weg hoeft? Zie dat je ’t doet.</p>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.5" n="5" rend="indent">Tot ziens,</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.6" n="6">T.t.</p>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.7" n="7">I.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.8" n="8">’t Boek v. <rs type="person" ref="bio.xml#pers035">Fromentin</rs> is goed.<ptr type="note" target="#note.orig.nl.2"/> ’t Andere is niet veel aan dunkt mij.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <pb xml:id="pb.orig.nl.2" f="2r" facs="#s2r" n="2"/>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.9" n="9">Mevrouw van Gogh</p>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.10" n="10">Villa Helma</p>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.11" n="11">Bussum</p>
            <pb xml:id="pb.orig.nl.3" f="2v" facs="#s2v" n="3"/>
         </div>
         <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
            <pb xml:id="pb.tr.en.1"
                corresp="#pb.orig.nl.1"
                f="1r"
                facs="#s1r"
                n="1"/>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.1" corresp="#p.orig.nl.1" n="1">Amst.</p>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.2" corresp="#p.orig.nl.2" n="2">Saturday</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.3" corresp="#p.orig.nl.3" n="3">Dearest Jo,</p>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.4" corresp="#p.orig.nl.4" n="4">Be so good as to come as soon as possible because I want to make a portrait of you.<ptr type="note" target="#note.tr.en.1"/> Arrange it if you can so that you don’t have to leave too early. See that you do.</p>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.5" corresp="#p.orig.nl.5" n="5" rend="indent">Until then,</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.6" corresp="#p.orig.nl.6" n="6">All yours</p>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.7" corresp="#p.orig.nl.7" n="7">I.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.8" corresp="#p.orig.nl.8" n="8">
               <rs type="person" ref="bio.xml#pers035">Fromentin</rs>’s book is good.<ptr type="note" target="#note.tr.en.2"/> I don’t think much of the other one.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <pb xml:id="pb.tr.en.2"
                corresp="#pb.orig.nl.2"
                f="2r"
                facs="#s2r"
                n="2"/>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.9" corresp="#p.orig.nl.9" n="9">Mevrouw van Gogh</p>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.10" corresp="#p.orig.nl.10" n="10">Villa Helma</p>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.11" corresp="#p.orig.nl.11" n="11">Bussum</p>
            <pb xml:id="pb.tr.en.3"
